rows.label: tlk44500189_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Everything you see here is treasure
that I personally collected over the
years. So go on, take a look!

rows.label: tlk44500189_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Go on. Take pity on this poor
man who finds it hard enough
to buy tomorrow's groceries.

rows.label: tlk44500189_01_msg0003
rows.name:
What kind souls! That should help me
with living expenses for a while!

rows.label: tlk44500189_01_msg0005
rows.name:
You becoming an owner has given
me a new lease on life. Things
are finally looking up.

rows.label: tlk44500189_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Please, take your time,
look around. You'll still
be paying, naturally.
